WEBVTT

0
00:00:02.568 --> 00:00:06.561
I'm Peppa Pig.
This is my little brother, George.

1
00:00:07.306 --> 00:00:08.432
This is Mummy Pig.

2
00:00:09.642 --> 00:00:10.939
And this is Daddy Pig.

3
00:00:13.312 --> 00:00:14.574
Peppa pig.

4
00:00:17.816 --> 00:00:19.943
Very Hot Day!

5
00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:24.016
The sun is shining.
It is a very hot day.

6
00:00:25.090 --> 00:00:26.819
What a Iovely, hot day!

7
00:00:28.727 --> 00:00:30.592
Peppa and George are
Wearing their boots!

8
00:00:30.829 --> 00:00:32.091
They are going to jump
in muddy puddles!

9
00:00:32.331 --> 00:00:34.094
I love muddy puddles.

10
00:00:35.834 --> 00:00:36.664
Oh!

11
00:00:36.902 --> 00:00:38.733
Oh, dear! The sun is so hot

12
00:00:38.904 --> 00:00:40.235
that the puddles have dried up!

13
00:00:41.340 --> 00:00:42.329
Mummy! Daddy!

14
00:00:42.675 --> 00:00:46.111
The puddles are all dry and
We can't jump in them!

15
00:00:46.412 --> 00:00:48.676
Never mind, Peppa.
It's so sunny,

16
00:00:49.048 --> 00:00:51.175
you can play in the
paddling pool instead!

17
00:00:51.617 --> 00:00:53.244
Yes! The paddling pool!

18
00:00:54.753 --> 00:00:57.187
First, you have to change into
your swimming costumes.

19
00:00:57.356 --> 00:00:58.482
Yes, Mummy.

20
00:01:04.630 --> 00:01:06.757
Peppa and George are Wearing
their swimming costumes!

21
00:01:07.566 --> 00:01:08.999
Mummy Pig is Wearing her
swimming costume.

22
00:01:09.568 --> 00:01:11.365
And Daddy Pig is Wearing his
swimming costume!

23
00:01:12.638 --> 00:01:15.505
Because it's so hot,
you need sun cream.

24
00:01:19.778 --> 00:01:21.871
It's all
oily and yucky!

25
00:01:25.517 --> 00:01:26.279
Yuck!

26
00:01:27.886 --> 00:01:29.376
What a fuss about nothing!

27
00:01:29.888 --> 00:01:32.220
Yes, We all need
sun cream today.

28
00:01:33.392 --> 00:01:34.017
Oh!

29
00:01:39.665 --> 00:01:40.393
Come on, George.

30
00:01:43.035 --> 00:01:44.798
Let's get some air into
this paddling pool!

31
00:01:46.038 --> 00:01:47.903
Daddy Pig is pumping up
the paddling pool!

32
00:01:51.610 --> 00:01:53.908
Easy as pie!

33
00:02:00.619 --> 00:02:04.248
Peppa holds the hose
and Mummy Pig turns on the Water.

34
00:02:06.558 --> 00:02:07.923
Where's the Water?

35
00:02:10.562 --> 00:02:11.688
Wahhh!

36
00:02:23.075 --> 00:02:25.839
Peppa and George love
their paddling pool.

37
00:02:26.211 --> 00:02:28.076
lce cream!
lce cream!

38
00:02:28.213 --> 00:02:30.272
Ms. Rabbit, the ice cream lady!

39
00:02:32.584 --> 00:02:33.573
lce cream!

40
00:02:34.086 --> 00:02:36.452
On very hot days,
Ms. Rabbit sells ice cream.

41
00:02:36.955 --> 00:02:38.217
Mummy, Daddy!

42
00:02:38.524 --> 00:02:40.583
Can George and I have
an ice cream, please?

43
00:02:40.793 --> 00:02:43.956
Oh, Well, I suppose it is
an especially hot day.

44
00:02:44.096 --> 00:02:45.085
Hurray!

45
00:02:45.731 --> 00:02:47.289
Please, can I have one as Well?

46
00:02:47.733 --> 00:02:49.360
Everyone likes ice cream!

47
00:02:49.802 --> 00:02:51.736
Hello, Mummy Pig,
Peppa and George.

48
00:02:51.870 --> 00:02:52.859
Hello, Ms. Rabbit.

49
00:02:53.472 --> 00:02:54.962
What ice creams
Would you like?

50
00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:57.674
Can I have a cone, please,
Ms. Rabbit?

51
00:02:57.876 --> 00:02:59.309
Of course you may, Peppa!

52
00:02:59.611 --> 00:03:00.373
Thank you.

53
00:03:00.979 --> 00:03:03.607
The same for me and
one for Daddy Pig, please.

54
00:03:04.983 --> 00:03:07.110
And What Would young
Mr. George like?

55
00:03:07.753 --> 00:03:08.879
Dine-Saw!

56
00:03:09.121 --> 00:03:10.053
A dinosaur?

57
00:03:10.689 --> 00:03:11.621
Silly George!

58
00:03:12.491 --> 00:03:15.756
He always says
''dinosaur'' for everything!

59
00:03:16.895 --> 00:03:17.759
Well, it just so happens

60
00:03:17.996 --> 00:03:20.897
that I do have a
dinosaur shaped ice-Iolly!

61
00:03:22.768 --> 00:03:25.396
Dine-Saw! Grrrr!

62
00:03:25.637 --> 00:03:26.262
George,

63
00:03:26.405 --> 00:03:28.498
you should eat your
ice-Iolly before it melts.

64
00:03:29.141 --> 00:03:30.403
Dine-Saw.

65
00:03:30.709 --> 00:03:33.007
George loves his dinosaur
ice-Iolly so much,

66
00:03:33.278 --> 00:03:34.142
he doesn't Want to eat it.

67
00:03:34.780 --> 00:03:35.769
Thank you, Ms. Rabbit!

68
00:03:36.148 --> 00:03:37.206
Enjoy the Weather!

69
00:03:39.651 --> 00:03:41.915
George, I really think you
should eat your ice-Iolly

70
00:03:42.087 --> 00:03:46.148
before it melts and...
falls on the ground.

71
00:03:47.726 --> 00:03:50.524
Oh, dear, George's dinosaur
ice-Iolly has melted

72
00:03:50.662 --> 00:03:51.356
and fallen on the ground.

73
00:03:51.797 --> 00:03:54.732
Come on, George.
You can share Daddy's ice cream.

74
00:03:55.033 --> 00:03:56.091
I'm sure he Won't mind.

75
00:04:00.806 --> 00:04:01.670
It is so Warm,

76
00:04:01.940 --> 00:04:03.237
Daddy Pig has fallen asleep!

77
00:04:03.609 --> 00:04:05.099
Daddy Pig does look hot!

78
00:04:05.444 --> 00:04:08.038
Let's tip Water on Daddy
to cool him down!

79
00:04:08.380 --> 00:04:09.438
Good idea, Peppa!

80
00:04:10.949 --> 00:04:12.883
What happened?!!!

81
00:04:13.185 --> 00:04:15.176
You Were all red
and hot, Daddy Pig!

82
00:04:15.387 --> 00:04:17.184
So We tipped Water on you!

83
00:04:17.322 --> 00:04:20.120
Oh, I see. Thank you, Peppa.

84
00:04:24.329 --> 00:04:26.058
Look! The puddles are back!

85
00:04:26.765 --> 00:04:28.699
Quick, George, let's get out boots!

86
00:04:33.772 --> 00:04:35.706
Peppa and George are
Wearing their boots!

87
00:04:37.843 --> 00:04:39.401
Peppa and George love the hot day.

88
00:04:39.978 --> 00:04:40.467
But most of all,

89
00:04:40.646 --> 00:04:42.580
they love jumping up
and down in puddles!

